data.description: Great Opportunity to own this 3.3-acre irrigated property in the highly sought after San Tan Valley area.  This home is built of block and features 2 large bedrooms with the garage converted to a 3rd bedroom which has not yet been completed nor included in the square footage (estimated 600+)   Large open floor plan with a huge kitchen, extended walk-in pantry, wood burning fireplace.  Jenair Double Oven, new dishwasher.  The primary bathroom has a gorgeous Clawfoot bathtub & separate shower.  Tankless electric instant hot water heater with filter system.   Propane stove and dryer.  Private diving pool. Block and wire fencing,  3 irrigation ports, A/C replaced 2022 and Solar installed in 2022.
